sentences.english: Thellonking is one of the most productive activities a human being can undertake.
sentences.chinese: 念考是此中最出产性活动己的总称能够举行。

sentences.english: In order to prepare for the rush from the hall after the notice, has been late.
sentences.chinese: 张伯为准备从后厅赶上去通知，己经晚了。

sentences.english: He has gone through two pairs of shoes since he went into winter training.
sentences.chinese: 自从他参加冬季体育训练以来己跑坏了两双鞋子。

sentences.english: Oneself are beautiful, said, flower flower also is drunk, why attached to an end?
sentences.chinese: 己说，花开是美，花落亦是醉，何必执着于一种结局？

sentences.english: Free of charge to help customers into the production process.
sentences.chinese: 该工艺非常成熟，己帮多家知名企业导入生产。

sentences.english: Since then the number of milu deer there has greatly increased.
sentences.chinese: 从那以后，那儿的糜鹿的数量己大大增加了。

sentences.english: Except otherwise stated, performance does take into account of reinvestments and capital gain or loss.
sentences.chinese: 除注明外，表现己考虑股息再投资及资本增长及损失。

sentences.english: The perpetration of the crime by the accused was proved to the satisfaction of the court.
sentences.chinese: 法庭确认被告的罪行己得到充分的证实。

sentences.english: Study on the catalytic synthesis of ethyl caproate by sodium hydrogen sulfate;
sentences.chinese: 目的研究硫酸氢钾在合成己酸己酯工艺中的催化性能。

sentences.english: These three mirrors I have always cherished.
sentences.chinese: 朕当常保此三镜，以防己过。

sentences.english: You started to play hi-fis since you were a student. Has your attitude changed since then?
sentences.chinese: 由学生时代己开始玩音响，到今天的心态可有转变？

sentences.english: Apart from his study, he is indifferent to everything because he comes from a defunct family.
sentences.chinese: 除此以外，他对所有无关于己的事情漠不关心。

sentences.english: As though some ballad singer had sung it all.
sentences.chinese: 仿佛某个民谣歌手己把它全部唱完。

sentences.english: My husband has grey in his hair.
sentences.chinese: 我的丈夫己经长出了灰发。

sentences.english: Who seeks more than ha has hinder himself from enjoying what he has.
sentences.chinese: 有了还追求更多的人，会防害自己享受己有的。

sentences.english: Non-invasive measurement of blood oxygen saturation has been widely used in clinic medicine.
sentences.chinese: 血氧饱和度的无创检测己在临床医学中得到广泛应用。
